webpackJsonp([0xa18a708f9a2d],{4911:function(e,t){e.exports={pathContext:{group:[{node:{fields:{title:"Wrong Passport",date:"07 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-07-wrong-passport/",tags:"Y2007"},html:"<p>From a <a href=\"http://www.dw-world.de/dw/article/0,,2338613,00.html\">Deutsche Welle analysis of the Kurnaz case</a>:</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n  Legally, Berlin was under no obligation to protect a German-born Turkish citizen imprisoned in Guantanamo. But moral and political responsibility for a permanent resident unjustly detained is another matter, experts say.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>Um, right, like the German government is going to lift a finger for <em>me</em> if I ever get in trouble. Let's just say that if I've got one phone call before I get shipped to the Gulag, I'm calling the embassy with the blue passports, not the one with the red passports.</p>"},next:{fields:{title:"Conscientious Objector",date:"07 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-07-conscientious-objector/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Hello World, We're Here Again",date:"09 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-09-hello-world-were-here-again/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Conscientious Objector",date:"07 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-07-conscientious-objector/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>In case you wonder why developers are so difficult to work with, <a href="http://lumma.de/eintrag.php?id=3248">Nico heard this</a> in our office in Cologne:</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n  I reject <a href="http://www.rubyonrails.org/">Ruby on Rails</a> for reasons of conscience.\n</p></blockquote>\n<p>Try explaining that to a client when your project is late and over budget. "We could have used a better framework, but our development team thought it was immoral."</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Attitude",date:"06 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-06-attitude/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Wrong Passport",date:"07 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-07-wrong-passport/"}}},{node:{fields:{title:"Attitude",date:"06 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-06-attitude/",tags:"Y2007"},html:'<p>After<a href="http://www.papascott.de/archives/2007/02/05/traction-times-ten/"> pissing and moaning yesterday</a> about my back, I slept through the night last night and feel pretty good today. Letting off steam helps (as does a pillow for the legs and new exercises).</p>\n<p>Oh, and welcome to the new <a href="http://cutline.tubetorial.com/">look</a>.</p>'},next:{fields:{title:"Traction Times Ten",date:"05 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-05-traction-times-ten/"}},previous:{fields:{title:"Conscientious Objector",date:"07 Feb 2007",slug:"/2007-02-07-conscientious-objector/"}}}],pathPrefix:"",first:!1,last:!1,index:157,pageCount:1101}}}});
